  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/0d81f3838fb89a6532843afe58b62ffd.poster.avif?t=1759156516\" width=500 height=241 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/0d81f3838fb89a6532843afe58b62ffd.webm?t=1759156516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make your Build</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/4e979a18327fdd634ad15d979c9bf239.poster.avif?t=1759156516\" width=450 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/4e979a18327fdd634ad15d979c9bf239.webm?t=1759156516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/4e979a18327fdd634ad15d979c9bf239.mp4?t=1759156516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start by choosing your character! We have some of the <strong>cutest and fiercest</strong> cats at your disposal. Each one has its own <strong>unique bonus</strong>, so choose wisely! After that, you'll need to equip your magic staff and accessory; they all have <strong>unique abilities</strong>, so you can <strong>mix and match to create unique combinations</strong>! If you like something, you can <strong>upgrade it to its full potential</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose your Cards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/b52a04576f2d923e8d845c8303177d45.poster.avif?t=1759156516\" width=450 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/b52a04576f2d923e8d845c8303177d45.webm?t=1759156516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/b52a04576f2d923e8d845c8303177d45.mp4?t=1759156516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After defeating a wave of enemies, you'll choose a card from a deck to upgrade your cat or staff, which will help you on your journey out of the catacombs.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat Bosses on Each Floor</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/62685488a684ac00e04aadd8999c34eb.poster.avif?t=1759156516\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/62685488a684ac00e04aadd8999c34eb.webm?t=1759156516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/62685488a684ac00e04aadd8999c34eb.mp4?t=1759156516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you reach the end of the floor, you'll face the boss, which will be randomly selected from three existing bosses, each with their own unique skills. Make no mistake, the same boss on higher floors also means more danger, even with the same attacks.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In-Game Content</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 Cats, each with a different playstyle;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 Staffs, each with a different power;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 Accessories, with different effects;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade system;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 Floor Bosses;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 Final Boss;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Codex with the number of enemies defeated, bosses, weapon usage information, and number of cards collected;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 Friendly Rat;</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If it caught your eye, don't forget to add it to your wish list!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/5fef3e764d8de68395cebce6bd13dbb8.webp?t=1759156516\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/5fef3e764d8de68395cebce6bd13dbb8.poster.avif?t=1759156516\" class=\"bb_img\" width=451 height=225 /></picture></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/0d81f3838fb89a6532843afe58b62ffd.poster.avif?t=1759156516\" width=500 height=241 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/0d81f3838fb89a6532843afe58b62ffd.webm?t=1759156516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make your Build</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/4e979a18327fdd634ad15d979c9bf239.poster.avif?t=1759156516\" width=450 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/4e979a18327fdd634ad15d979c9bf239.webm?t=1759156516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452890/extras/4e979a18327fdd634ad15d979c9bf239.mp4?t=1759156516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start by choosing your character! We have some of the <strong>cutest and fiercest</strong> cats at your disposal. Each one has its own <strong>unique bonus</strong>, so choose wisely! After that, you'll need to equip your magic staff and accessory; they all have <strong>unique abilities</strong>, so you can <strong>mix and match to create unique combinations</strong>! If you like something, you can <strong>upgrade it to its full potential</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose your Cards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.